Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,およそ遠しとされしもの　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:47.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見慣れた動植物とは　まるで違うと　おぼしきモノ達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヒトは古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ この匂いは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:32.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,濃い 果実酒のような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒？ こんな所に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや 違うな 饐えたような匂いになった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:54.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,匂いの源に 何がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちを 見ている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:08.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,体が竦む 動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よーし そのままだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ 人か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあいい 見逃してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,楽になった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ 今のは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:41.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,猟師？ いや　丸切り手ぶらだった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:46.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それに 甘い匂いが消えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは 一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:06.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか昨日は疲れたな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちっと精の付くもん食うか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,干し肉はねえだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:27.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや ここんとこ 獲物はさっぱりでな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:33.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかい 向こうにあんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,止めとけな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつんとこの肉は 臭くて敵わんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:50.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,確かに 少し腐ったような…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,新しいのはねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家になら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっちを分けちゃもらえんか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいよ ついてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家ん中からも腐臭は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今朝狩ってきた獲物 分けてくれって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,構わねえが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体誰だ？ 珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,腐臭に混ざって 甘い匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:41.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昨日 山で嗅いだあの匂いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:50.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やあ 旅の人かい 上がりなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どれでも好きなの持ってくといい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昨日の晩 山で狩りを？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ 今朝捌いたばかりだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:06.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ その肉はずっと日にでも晒してたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:10.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたも 家の獲物が臭えってのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこかだよ 全然匂わねぇじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なあ 卯介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ いいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ 今から狩ってきてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなら 文句はねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何 半時もあれば済む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこで少し 待っててくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちだ 来い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:07:01.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだ そのままだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,止せ　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もういい　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:20.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんの狩った獲物は どんなに新しくとも 不味いはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,意のままに獲物を狩る手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:30.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,血筋に 同じ手を持つ者はないか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ 親父もそうだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:38.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,掌に 眼玉のような痣があるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:43.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつは 腐酒というものに冒されてる印だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,腐酒というのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:55.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,生命の素たるもの 光酒の腐れてしまったものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本来 成るはずの蟲と成れず
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤い泥状となり 地下水から地上に湧き出る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:07.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,果実酒のような匂いがするが 毒性があり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,高い濃度で口にすれば 死に至る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:17.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが 極稀に 毒に耐える体質の者がある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,腐酒単体には意思もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ただ 更なる腐敗を待つだけのものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,動物の体内に入り 血に紛れると 命を得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,宿主もまた 特殊な力を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:38.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,甘い匂いを掌から出し 獲物を引き付け 酔わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,容易く狩りをする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして それは血を介して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,子々孫々まで伝わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:51.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,へえ そういうもんだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ただ 力を得る者は極僅かだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,力を得なかった者は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,毒のため長くは生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃんは 血を吐いて死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,弟も同じ病だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それもその腐酒ってやつのせいなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,治してやる方法はないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ 卯介も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,安心しろ 治療法ならある
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:21.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,光酒を一定量飲めば 腐酒は消滅する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今は手持ちが足りねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:24.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,調達してこよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:28.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか よかったな 卯介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これでもう 苦しい思いをしねえで済むぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,治療が必要なのは 弟だけじゃねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺？ 俺は何ともねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんの父親 最後はどうなった？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:52.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,知ってるなら話は早い 早めに手を打ったほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな特別な力などなくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんだけ立派な体がありゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,兄弟で食ってくだけの狩りはできるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それじゃ二人分な
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一月程度で持ってこれると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よろしく頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それまでまた 間違って人を狩ろうとするなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしかして 昨夜会ったの　あんただったか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃ悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつも日が落ちてから狩りをするのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:31.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ 獣は夜歩き回るやつが多い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昼間多いのは 夜目の利かねえ鳥くらいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,小鳥など狩っても つまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:43.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら 提灯くらい持ってくれ 紛らわしいし 不用心だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,火があっちゃ 獣が寄り付かねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この山なら 目をつぶってても歩けるし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺を襲う獣もいねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,月の光で十分なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は 山の王にでもなったつもりか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も山の一部にすぎんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何で命を落とすかなど 誰にも知れんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:15.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,たとえ それが山で最も恐れられる 獣だとしてもな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ 肝に銘じとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:27.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと 薬飲んでくれるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺 元の辰兄に戻って欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:42.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ 俺は別に何も変わらんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ギンコさん 薬は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ 手に入れた 兄貴は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,狩りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,相変わらずだな こんな宵の口に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一緒に来て 早く辰兄に 薬あげて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは… みんな辰がやったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:10.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんがいなくなってから 辰兄は父ちゃんに似てきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:16.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんも よくこんな余分な狩りをしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:28.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そら 持って帰って捌いとけ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃん まだ家にいっぱいあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら売ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,みんな 臭くて要らないって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら そこらに捨てておけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:45.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄 父ちゃんなんでこんなことするのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:51.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんは 生きてるものを狩ること自体が好きなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんに逆らうな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺らも いつ狩られっか分かんねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:01.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,危ねえと思ったら 母ちゃんみてえに逃げるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,怖かねえよ 俺にだって力はあんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は俺が守ってやっから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:16.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんの異変が始まったのは そんなある日だった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:20.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃん変だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,体の向こうが 透けて見える
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃん 影がない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして あの日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃん 朝飯だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:57.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんは 消えてなくなってしまってた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分より強い先代がいなくなると
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,枷が外れたように  その子孫の力が増すという
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,腐酒の侵食が進み
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて 体を完全に乗っ取られる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,つまり 完全に蟲の側に行っちまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父親は死んだわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,実体をなくし 心もなくして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今も 山を彷徨っているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:37.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄も このままじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,甘い…匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:51.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やあ 戻ったのかい ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ 光酒は手に入れた 早く飲め
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,卯介に 飲ませといてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:05.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺は また気が向いた時にするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:11.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山に君臨する気分ってのは ずいぶんといいもんらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが目を覚ませ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:18.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は 意思すら持たねえ蟲に踊らされてるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うるせえな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:26.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた 自分の立場分かってんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,卯介の薬だけ置いてってやってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺はなぁ もう二度と御免なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:42.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,親父がいた頃みてえに 狩られるかもしれねえ側に戻るなんてな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄 止めてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,怖いことなんてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺 襲われない方法知ってから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこへ行った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻らねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:27.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,元の俺に戻ってやらねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,卯介？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:45.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を撃った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,熊だと思うが 崖から落ちちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:02.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,腐酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:13.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,くそ 腕が動かねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ 獣にやられちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここで 朝まで待つか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夜がこんなに 長いとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,闇がこんなに 恐ろしいとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここだ 卯介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,待て 出てくるな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:20.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,鳥どもは なんで 俺の腕を…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:27.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,動物 中でも特に鳥類は 目玉文様に恐れを抱く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:30.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,果実の匂いに引き寄せられても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:35.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これまで掌の文様のために 襲えずにいたのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,目玉が血で隠れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:43.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その腕は 鳥にとって甘美な餌となったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,鳥の餌か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄 だいぶ熱下がったね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前 ずいぶん顔色よくなったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だろう もうずっと血を吐かない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと 光酒ってのが効いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:05.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺も狩り覚えるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:09.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,辰兄も 早く元気になって 一緒にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:20.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:35.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだよ 嚇かすない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:43.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,闇の中では 誰しも何かの影に怯える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:50.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,闇に遊び 踊り戯れるのは異形ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:57.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしも 真に夜の異形の王がいたんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やはり あんな風なのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,鏡が淵
